term.privacy.paragraph.item2: Registration Information: When you register as our member, we may collect necessary registration information such as your name, email address, residential address, and phone number. Facebook Login Information: If you log in through Facebook, we may obtain your public information on Facebook, including but not limited to profile information, friend list, and contact information. Usage Information: We may automatically collect usage information, including IP address, access time, and browser type, to optimize user experience.
term.privacy.paragraph.item3: Providing Services: The collected information will be used to provide, maintain, and improve our services, ensuring a safe and efficient user experience. Personalized Services: We may use your information to provide personalized content, recommendations, or advertisements, and to improve service quality. Use of Facebook Login Information: We will only use Facebook login information when necessary and will not post any information on your Facebook account without your consent.
term.privacy.paragraph.item4: Third-Party Sharing: We will not sell, trade, or transfer your personal information to third parties unless with your consent or as required by law. Compliance Disclosure: We will disclose necessary information as required by law to respond to legal processes, court orders, or to protect the rights of ourselves and other users.
term.privacy.paragraph.item5: Security Measures: We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. Data Storage: Your information may be stored on our servers or on secure servers of our partners.
term.privacy.paragraph.item6: Use of Cookies: We may use cookies and similar technologies to enhance user experience, but you can configure the settings in your browser.
term.privacy.paragraph.item7: Policy Changes: We reserve the right to modify this privacy policy, and the updated policy will be published on our website.
term.privacy.paragraph.item8: Personal Data Rights: You have the right to inquire, correct, delete your personal information, and to object to or restrict its processing. To exercise these rights, please contact us.
term.privacy.paragraph.item9: If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us.
